data.title: FAPCCI Membership Directory 2008-09 - Final
data.meta_description: FAPCCI Membership Directory 2008-09_Final - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of 151 company names with no other information provided about the companies. The names appear to be Indian companies from various industries ranging from power, infrastructure, pharmaceuticals, cement, and others. No other context or high level summary can be discerned from the raw company name listing.
